In-Cookie Session
=================

Store session in signed cookie.

Basic Usage
-----------

// just include session class
require_once 'session.php';

// start session normally
start_session();

// Read and write in session
$_SESSION['foo'] = 'bar';

// juste before output, call session_write_close
session_write_close();

// now session data have been send to the client via signed cookie. You cannot write on $_SESSION.

echo 'Hello Word';

